OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny evening
OL,6,Fbrightness will be short-lived as
OL,7,Fcloud and light rain moves in from the
OL,8,Fwest. Turning breezy through late
OL,9,Fevening before a band of heavier and
OL,10,Fmore persistent rain spreads northeast
OL,11,Fafter midnight, rain easing by dawn.
OL,12,FMild.
OL,13,
OL,14,CWednesday:FCloudy start, with some
OL,15,Fearly light rain in the south. Some
OL,16,Fwarmer, drier intervals developing
OL,17,Fbefore heavy rain and gusty winds move
OL,18,Feast through the afternoon, clearing
OL,19,Fto showers later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
